		<p class="post-categories"><a href="http://werblog.com/category/uncategorized/">Uncategorized</a></p>
		
	</div>
	
</div>

<div id="post-75" class="cf post-75 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

	<h2>
		<span class="post-format"></span>
		<a href="http://werblog.com/2002/06/what-is-the-consume-project/" title="&quot;What is the Consume project?" rel="bookmark">&quot;What is the Consume project?</a>
		
	</h2>

	
	
	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Jun</p>
			<p class="post-day">28</p>
			<p class="post-year">2002</p>				
		</div>

		&#8220;What is the Consume project? Consume is a collaborative strategy for the self provision of a broadband telecommunications infrastructure.&#8221;
		
	</div>

	<div class="post-footer">
		<a class="post-readmore" href="http://werblog.com/2002/06/what-is-the-consume-project/" title="&quot;What is the Consume project?">
